data.description: Huge Price Reduction!! Nice lot with a lot of potential near Deer Point Lake. The lot is mainly clear with the exception of being a little over grown. There is access to Deer Point Lake through an easement at the end of Blue Gill Rd. There once was a home on the lot so there is a well and Septic on the property with access to electrical hook up. This will be a great Lot to build a nice Home or place a Manufactured Home. Across from this lot there is a .45 acre lot that is available as well. See MLS 745791. Drive by and Take a Look. Seller is motivated and will consider all offers.
